<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><p>Ensuring the existence and accuracy of references in scientific writing is critical for maintaining the integrity of academic work. This paper highlights the risks of unverified citations and demonstrates the need for automated tools to detect invalid references.</p></div>
